Contains the following Games:-Sonic the Hedgehog 1,2&3,Sonic Spinball,Sonic 3D blast,Knuckles Chaotic 32x,Knuckles in Sonic 2&3

Installation Details:-
1.Run setup.exe file
2.click Install
3.Controls are --i)Pause-->Enter
                 ii)Spin-->Spacebar
                 iii)Jump-->Left Ctrl,Left Shift
                  iv)Up,Down,Left,Right Movement-->Arrow Buttons.
